'''美国-荷兰关系'''是[[荷兰|荷兰]]和[[美国|美国]]之间的双边关系。[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]<ref>[https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/3204.htm U.S. Relations With the Netherlands] {{Wayback|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/3204.htm |date=20190604190845 }}, ''[[Bureau_of_European_and_Eurasian_Affairs|Bureau of European and Eurasian Affairs]]''.</ref>和荷兰外交部均认为两国关系非常好。<ref>[https://www.government.nl/topics/international-relations/overview-countries-and-regions/united-states Relations between the Netherlands and the United States of America] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819062358/https://www.government.nl/topics/international-relations/overview-countries-and-regions/united-states |date=2017-08-19 }}, ''Rijksoverheid''.</ref>两国于1782年建立官方关系，由于两国从未发生过战争或严重冲突，1982年美国总统[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]称两国关系是“我们与其他任何国家之间持续时间最长的和平关系”。<ref>[http://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/ws/?pid=42416 Remarks at the Welcoming Ceremony for Queen Beatrix of the Netherlands] {{Wayback|url=http://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/ws/?pid=42416 |date=20180614150438 }}, ''The American President Project''</ref>近几十年来，两国在反恐、反海盗和欧洲、中东和中美洲地区的维和任务（主要通过[[北约|北约]]）方面进行了大量合作。他们也是彼此经济的第三大直接外国投资者。
